@startuml
title Diagramme de composants - Plateforme E-Services

left to right direction

skinparam defaultFontSize 10
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam nodesep 22
skinparam ranksep 30
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

scale 0.82

actor "Navigateur" as Nav

rectangle "Plateforme E-Services" {
  component "reverse-proxy\n<<Nginx>>\n(optionnel)" as RP
  component "frontend-spa\n<<React>>" as FE
  component "backend-api\n<<Laravel PHP>>" as BE
  database "base-postgresql\n<<PostgreSQL>>" as PG
  component "stockage-fichiers\n<<volume Docker>>" as VOL
}

Nav --> RP : HTTPS (cookies Secure)
RP --> FE : assets statiques
RP --> BE : HTTPS /api/ (Cookie session)

BE --> PG : JDBC SQL + sessions
BE --> VOL : fichiers pieces jointes

note bottom of BE
  Auth par cookies : session serveur, Set-Cookie
  SESSION HttpOnly Secure SameSite.
  Front : fetch avec credentials include.
  Pas de Bearer JWT sur ce schema.
end note

note bottom of RP
  Reverse-proxy : TLS et routage vers SPA et API.
end note

@enduml
